            "title": "Expans\u00e3o da educa\u00e7\u00e3o secund\u00e1ria em Pernambuco : atores pol\u00edticos e a interioriza\u00e7\u00e3o dos gin\u00e1sios p\u00fablicos (1948-1963)",
            "abstract": [
                "This book is the result of several meetings. The first of them was on the floor of my school, during High School, where I heard, for the first time, that it was possible for students from Public Schools to enter Higher Education. Therefore, History was the path, the choice. In this path, I carry the commitment to history and education, which constitutes a field of research crossed by theoretical, personal, collective experiences and social principles. In order to understand and interpret events and stories about secondary schools in Pernambuco, particularly their social pressure to increase vacancies in public gymnasiums, I point out the following questions in this book: How did the expansion process of the first cycle of public secondary education occur in Pernambuco? How did state, municipal and federal political actors act in the creation of these educational establishments? What were the financing policies for the creation of these gyms? As Marc Bloch (1997, p. 17) says: \u201cIsn't it true that, in order to act wisely, it is necessary, first, to understand?\u201d. Thus, this book seeks to understand the role of the State in the process of democratization of schooling in Pernambuco society",
                "Este livro \u00e9 fruto de v\u00e1rios encontros. O primeiro deles foi no ch\u00e3o da minha escola, durante o Ensino M\u00e9dio, onde ouvi, pela primeira vez, que era poss\u00edvel alunos e alunas de Escolas P\u00fablicas ingressarem no Ensino Superior. Portanto, a Hist\u00f3ria foi o caminho, a escolha. Nesse caminho, carrego o compromisso com a hist\u00f3ria e a educa\u00e7\u00e3o, que constitui um campo de pesquisa atravessado por viv\u00eancias te\u00f3ricas, pessoais, coletivas e princ\u00edpios sociais. No sentido de compreender e interpretar acontecimentos e hist\u00f3rias sobre a escola secund\u00e1ria em Pernambuco particularmente da sua press\u00e3o social para a amplia\u00e7\u00e3o de vagas em gin\u00e1sios p\u00fablicos, aponto os seguintes questionamentos neste livro: Como ocorreu o processo de expans\u00e3o do primeiro ciclo do ensino secund\u00e1rio p\u00fablico em Pernambuco? Como os atores pol\u00edticos estaduais, municipais e federais atuaram na cria\u00e7\u00e3o desses estabelecimentos de ensino? Quais foram as pol\u00edticas de financiamento para a cria\u00e7\u00e3o desses gin\u00e1sios? Como diz Marc Bloch (1997, p. 17): \u201cn\u00e3o \u00e9 verdade que, para agir avisadamente, \u00e9 necess\u00e1rio, primeiro, compreender?\u201d. Assim, este livro busca compreender o papel do Estado no processo de democratiza\u00e7\u00e3o da escolariza\u00e7\u00e3o na sociedade pernambucana"
            ],
